  "title": "Senior Vaccum Piping Engineer",
  "description": "<p>🚀 We’re Hiring: Senior Vacuum Piping Engineer / Site Lead</p><p></p><p>📍 Location: Singapore</p><p>🏭 Industry: Semiconductor / Fab Construction / Facilities Engineering</p><p>🗓 Work Schedule: Monday to Friday</p><p>⏰ Working Hours: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🔧 About the Role</p><p></p><p>Our client is seeking a highly experienced Senior Vacuum Piping Engineer / Site Lead to take ownership of on-site vacuum piping (pumping line) works for semiconductor fabrication facilities.</p><p></p><p>This is a hands-on technical leadership role, ideal for professionals with deep fab experience who can lead site execution while coordinating closely with major semiconductor partners such as UMC, VSMC, and Micron.</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🔑 Key Responsibilities</p><p>•\tLead and oversee on-site vacuum piping (pumping line) installation and hook-up works</p><p>•\tDirect, coordinate, and supervise work crews to ensure quality, safety, and schedule compliance</p><p>•\tConduct site measurements, surveys, and routing planning based on drawings and site conditions</p><p>•\tEnsure installations comply with semiconductor fab standards and client specifications</p><p>•\tSource vacuum piping materials and components locally in Singapore</p><p>•\tCoordinate closely with project teams, subcontractors, and client representatives</p><p>•\tSupport testing, commissioning, and handover activities as required</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>✅ Requirements</p><p>•\tProven experience in vacuum piping systems for semiconductor fabrication facilities</p><p>•\tFamiliarity with fab environments and standards at UMC, VSMC, and/or Micron</p><p>•\tStrong site leadership experience managing and directing work crews</p><p>•\tAbility to read technical drawings, perform on-site measurements, and adapt routing as needed</p><p>•\tSolid knowledge of local sourcing for vacuum piping materials and components</p><p>•\tHands-on, proactive, and comfortable working in a fast-paced fab construction environment</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🎯 Preferred Background</p><p>•\tSemiconductor facilities engineering</p><p>•\tFab construction or line/system integration</p><p>•\tVacuum, gas, or process utility systems</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>✨ If you have strong semiconductor fab experience and are ready to lead critical vacuum piping works on-site, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p></p><p>📩 Apply now or reach out for a confidential discussion.</p>",
